    "一点一点重写, 直至其最终变为了一个值. 基于这种关系, "
    "我们定义了多步求值关系, 其允许我们讨论项(经过多步)求值至值. "
    "另一种风格被称为" (Em "大步") "语义 (或者有时说" (Em "自然语义")
    "), 其直接表述了" (Q "这个项求值至这个最终的值") "的概念, 记作" (&dArr $t $v)
    ". 对于我们的布尔和算术的表达式的语言而言的大步求值规则看起来如下:"
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-Value)")
         (&dArr $v $v))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-IfTrue)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 $true)
          (&dArr $t_2 $v_2)
          (&dArr (If $t_1 $t_2 $t_3) $v_2)))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-IfFalse)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 $false)
          (&dArr $t_3 $v_3)
          (&dArr (If $t_1 $t_2 $t_3) $v_3)))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-Succ)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 $nv_1)
          (&dArr (&succ $t_1) (&succ $nv_1))))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-PredZero)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 $zero)
          (&dArr (&pred $t_1) $zero)))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-PredSucc)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 (&succ $nv_1))
          (&dArr (&pred $t_1) $nv_1)))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-IsZeroZero)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 $zero)
          (&dArr (&iszero $t_1) $true)))
    (MBL (RuleLabel "(B-IsZeroSucc)")
         (&rule
          (&dArr $t_1 (&succ $nv_1))
          (&dArr (&iszero $t_1) $false)))
    "请表明对于这个语言而言, 其小步语义和大步语义是相合的, 即"
    (&->* $t $v) "当且仅当" (&dArr $t $v) ".")
